thread.title: Mark
thread.title_full: Wall Art Prints reviewed by Mark

author: Mark&Laura
title: Mark
text: It's so hard to get suppliers to deliver to Alice Springs. We have nothing here and are so far from metro areas, you would think suppliers would make it a point to deliver. Wall Art Prints have delivered my gorgeous prints quickly and they are beautiful. The only problem we had was a dislodged/broken side frame beam on the largest print, which my husband was luckily able to fix. Can't wait to show everyone. Thank you!
